com.capgemini.cobigen.impl.config

Class TemplatesConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.capgemini.cobigen.impl.config.TemplatesConfiguration

  • public class TemplatesConfiguration
extends Object
    The TemplatesConfiguration is a configuration data wrapper for all information of a context about templates and the target destination for the generated data.
